name: Ext_R5_Schedule_actor
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.Schedule.actor for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version extension represents Schedule.actor from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Schedule|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4B.

element.short: Resource(s) that availability information is being provided for
element.definition: Slots that reference this schedule resource provide the availability details to these referenced resource(s).
element.comment: `Schedule.actor` maps to R4B `Schedule.actor`. Type `Reference(http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/CareTeam)` has no mapping So is mapped as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget.
